{"tid":1169593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那補血劍】肖建華被帶走逾2年 旗下包商銀行被央行、銀保監接管","createTime":"2019-05-24T13:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T16:16:00.000Z","uid":13663,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"24c77b7d6f816b02d7615c552ffb4cb11824e6ce","tid":1169593,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:17:56.000Z","msg":"被喻為中共權貴白手套、明天系創辦人肖建華被中共有關部門，於2017年1月27日，從香港四季酒店帶回大陸接受調查，至今沒有消息。官媒今日宣佈，肖建華旗下核心金融機構之一「包商銀行」被央行及銀保監會接管。除了1998年被宣佈關閉後被接管、清算的海南發展銀行以外，這是中國20年來第一間被宣佈監管接管的商業銀行。<br />\n<br />\n央行、銀保監會今日聯合發表公告，稱鑑於包商銀行出現嚴重信用風險，為保護存款人和其他客戶合法權益，依照《中華人民共和國中國人民銀行法》、《中華人民共和國銀行業監督管理法》和《中華人民共和國商業銀行法》有關規定，銀保監會決定即日起，接管包商銀行1年。"},{"pid":"770a8dc198c60d3f922a28f47c20180e473f8d89","tid":1169593,"uid":2267,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"呢啲時期出呢啲新聞，香港班有錢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406f3867c045b12bab285c0e92e401fc91709347","tid":1169593,"uid":13663,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Qkxtv7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Qkxtv7.png&h=a07727f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MsAp34s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMsAp34s.png&h=5e7cbcdc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aff116141554efa6017f4c91cb393e3c66e681f","tid":1169593,"uid":253462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:31:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"294b53c2c56e2bfb53bc876cfa509b6cb776273b","tid":1169593,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下個到邊個"},{"pid":"6f24ffa025463bc318dc2f7e814d66f05ed51d26","tid":1169593,"